title: Jason_&_John_2014_Fishshitting_Entertainment_PDF
description:
From the Jason & John Info.txt

"Jason & John by Jimmy Rosano

This PDF file was a comic that I had done in the Spring of 2011. It was raining heavily at my warehouse space, which I had just moved into, and my room was filled with water. So for 3-5 days I spent writing and illustrating these two issues until the rain had stopped. The artwork was done with my non-dominant hand and the concept came from a more recent Cure album cover.

If you can find all the Random Word Placements, also known as RWPs, post your list on ShitGarden [http://shitgarden.proboards.com/] under the "Spam Visual" subfolder and as a reply on the thread "Jason & John RWP Findings". First to find all of them will receive a special gift from me. 

Donations are greatly appreciated via Bitcoin: 1PLizugj3zwuFFAXSNx3RwdxeCBh44AxR1"
